    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Formal descriptions of badges, banners, and  flags, or in heraldry, coats of arts, which enables a person to construct or recontruct the appopriate image.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000049955/Woodcock and Robinson, Oxford Guide to Heraldry (1988)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Formale Beschreibung eines Abzeichens, Banners oder einer Flagge bzw. eines Wappens in der Heraldik, welche die Anfertigung einer getreuen Abbildung ermöglichen soll.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Formele beschrijvingen van kentekens, banieren en vlaggen of in wapens of wapenschilden die iemand in staat stellen om het juiste beeld te construeren of te reconstrueren.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Descrições formais de insígnias, estandartes e bandeiras, ou em heráldica, brasões, que permitem a uma pessoa construir ou reconstruir a imagem apropriada.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
